snippet.title: Selena gomez rare beauty review || Amber Garcia
snippet.description:
Hi loves! Here is my raw opinion of the Selena Gomez rare beauty review. I gave my opinion of what I thought about it and thought I was really good, don't mind the terrible color match! LOL! Other than that I would recommend if you are looking into purchasing them. I will put everything down below in the description box of the products that I bought. Enjoy! :) #rarebeauty #makeupreview #selenagomezbeauty 

Products mentioned:

Liquid touch weightless foundation 
Liquid touch brightening concealer
Soft pink liquid blush  in the color Bliss
Optimist illuminating primer 
optimist 4 in 1 prime and set mist
Liquid touch concealer & foundation brush
